      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "An Ace Idea!",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Sup, Ace! Wanna get gnarly on\r\na Zinogre? It\u0027s been a while since\r\nwe hunted together and, as your\r\nmaster, I\u0027ve gotta keep tabs on\r\nmy favorite pupil\u0027s progress! You\u0027ve\r\nbeen in Elgado for a while now,\r\nso show me what you\u0027ve learned!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Une id\u00E9e d\u0027artiste !",
        "Client": "Utsushi le ma\u00EEtre",
        "Description": "H\u00E9, l\u0027artiste ! \u00C7a rigole\r\nplus ! On doit aller chasser\r\nun Zinogre ! \u00C7a fait un bail\r\nqu\u0027on a pas chass\u00E9 ensemble,\r\net faut que je me remette \u00E0\r\nchasser, alors montre-moi ce\r\nque t\u0027as appris \u00E0 Elgado !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Una rimpatriata vincente",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "Eccoti! Mettiamoci al lavoro!\r\n\u00C8 ora di cacciare uno Zinogre.\r\nNe \u00E8 passato di tempo dalla\r\nnostra ultima caccia e io ho\r\nbisogno di un po\u0027 di azione.\r\nMostrami le abilit\u00E0 che hai\r\nimparato a Elgado.",
        "Target": "Caccia uno Zinogre",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Alter und Ass",
        "Client": "Meister Utsushi",
        "Description": "Hey, Ass! M\u00F6chtest du einem\r\nZinogre auf die Pelle r\u00FCcken?\r\nEs ist eine Weile her, dass wir\r\nzusammen gejagt haben \u2013\r\nund mich interessiert dein\r\nFortschritt! Zeig mir, was du\r\nso in Elgado gelernt hast!",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Zinogre.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "\u00A1Qu\u00E9 pacha, hacha!",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "\u00A1Qu\u00E9 pasa, hacha! \u00BFQuieres\r\nsacudir a un Zinogre? \u00A1Hace\r\ntiempo que no cazamos juntos,\r\ncomo maestro tuyo tengo\r\nque observar tu progreso!\r\n\u00A1Demu\u00E9strame qu\u00E9 has aprendido\r\nen Elgado!",
        "Target": "Caza un Zinogre",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
